## Remotion Package Notes

This project uses a fixed set of packages. Do not install new packages without confirming with the user.

Available already:
- `remotion` — core (interpolate, spring, Audio, staticFile, Sequence, Series…)
- `@remotion/media-utils` — audio visualization (`npx remotion add @remotion/media-utils` if not yet installed)

Forbidden in this project:
- `@remotion/google-fonts` — use `waitForInter()` from `./fonts` instead
- `@remotion/motion-blur` — not installed
- `@remotion/three` — 3D transforms are forbidden across the entire project
- `@remotion/noise` — use `Math.sin(frame * seed)` for deterministic pseudo-noise
 
